com.stormpath.sdk.group

Interface GroupMembership

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Deletable, Resource

    public interface GroupMembership
extends Resource, Deletable
    A GroupMembership represents the association of an Account and a Group.

    Deleting this resource will only delete the association - it will not delete either the Account or Group.

    Since:
    0.4
